| products = [[Set-top boxes]]<br />[[Digital Video Recorders]]<br />[[Interactive television]] <br/>Compact Television head-ends <br />[[Residential gateway|Residential Gateways]], <br />[[Home network|Home Networking]], <br />[[TR-069]] Remote Management, <br />[[Mesh Technology]]
